WEBVTT

00:00.125 --> 00:02.352
<i>Previously on The Last Man On Earth...</i>

00:02.377 --> 00:04.146
ERICA: <i>Another painless birth, huh?</i>

00:04.171 --> 00:07.039
CAROL: <i>Would you believe it was
even easier than the first one?</i>

00:07.074 --> 00:10.075
Melissa, I don't need kids to
be happy. All I need is you.

00:10.110 --> 00:12.335
- You are the snake?
- PANCHO: I thought you knew.

00:12.360 --> 00:14.010
You were going to let
me hit the piñata.

00:14.035 --> 00:16.102
HECTOR: <i>The bomb is
not in the piñata.</i>

00:16.126 --> 00:17.260
PANCHO: <i>Then where is it?</i>

00:20.469 --> 00:22.154
(WOMEN SPEAKING BABY TALK)

