(INDISTINCT TALKING)

00:26.070 --> 00:28.070
Guys. Guys.

00:28.231 --> 00:29.964
I did it.

00:35.803 --> 00:36.768
(HIGH-PITCHED): Boop.

00:36.804 --> 00:40.286
(LAUGHS) I finished a whole side.

00:40.311 --> 00:42.958
Guys, come on, look at how smart I am.

00:42.983 --> 00:44.098
Guys?

00:44.123 --> 00:46.438
Tandy, I have a question...
if you're so smart,

00:46.463 --> 00:47.999
why are you calling us "guys"?

00:48.048 --> 00:49.701
Yeah, it's just what
you say when you want

00:49.716 --> 00:50.949
to get a bunch of people's attention.

00:50.984 --> 00:54.368
Yeah, but we're all women...
and now with the twins and Dawn,

00:54.393 --> 00:56.393
there's seven ladies and only three men.

00:56.418 --> 00:58.293
I mean, we more than double you.

00:58.318 --> 01:01.309
Don't you think calling us
"guys" is a little sexist?

01:01.334 --> 01:03.477
(CHUCKLES): Uh, I can't be sexist.

01:03.502 --> 01:07.080
Okay? I am a father of two baby women.

01:07.105 --> 01:09.510
I mean, I think girls are
so nice I made 'em twice.

01:09.535 --> 01:12.025
- Whatever, Tandy.
- What? Uh, no, seriously,

01:12.050 --> 01:13.783
I am super pro-lady.

01:13.808 --> 01:15.090
I wouldn't lie to you guys.

01:15.115 --> 01:16.152
- Tandy!
- There it is.

01:16.184 --> 01:17.261
Sexist pig.

01:17.286 --> 01:19.386
No, no, no, no, no.
You're absolutely right.

01:19.421 --> 01:21.635
We are living in a brave new world,

01:21.660 --> 01:25.095
where there are more hot
dog buns than hot dogs.

01:25.120 --> 01:26.955
So if I have offended you guys at all...

01:26.980 --> 01:29.159
- WOMEN: Tandy!
- Oh, I did it again!

01:29.191 --> 01:31.744
That... I... that was my bad.

01:31.769 --> 01:33.667
Look, this is a problem, okay?

01:33.702 --> 01:36.503
And it will not stand.

01:36.923 --> 01:39.272
(HUFFING BREATHS)

01:41.603 --> 01:42.676
How about this?

01:43.431 --> 01:45.032
From now on,

01:45.087 --> 01:48.009
anytime we would normally say "guys,"

01:48.337 --> 01:50.050
we'll say "gals" instead.

01:50.085 --> 01:51.087
This'll last a day.

01:51.112 --> 01:53.119
Uh, no, uh, no, it won't.

01:53.188 --> 01:56.056
Huh? This is gonna
last a lifetime. Yeah.

01:56.091 --> 01:58.959
Hey, got an ultra-serious
question for you.

02:00.126 --> 02:01.548
What's got two thumbs

02:01.573 --> 02:04.474
and a deep respect for gender equality?

02:06.001 --> 02:07.868
This gal.

02:09.003 --> 02:10.342
This gal.

02:10.366 --> 02:12.706
That's not gonna get annoying at all.

02:12.741 --> 02:13.506
Hey, Gail?

02:13.531 --> 02:14.975
Gail? Gail?

02:15.010 --> 02:16.643
Yeah, on that,

02:16.678 --> 02:19.079
