02:19.114 --> 02:21.014
Agree-men-t?

02:21.049 --> 02:22.048
Nah.

02:22.428 --> 02:24.784
Agreewomen-t.

02:24.820 --> 02:26.592
Yeah, that's my current jam.

02:26.617 --> 02:29.618
And I look forward to
spreading it on all your bread.

02:32.374 --> 02:33.927
Idiot.

