have too many blueberries.

02:51.271 --> 02:53.031
Hmm? Maybe I should eat a few.

02:53.056 --> 02:54.343
Let me see that. Mm.

02:54.368 --> 02:57.442
- (MOCK GOBBLING)
- Um, Todd?

02:57.478 --> 02:58.543
- (GRUNTING)
- Todd.

02:58.579 --> 03:00.312
Uh?

03:00.347 --> 03:02.481
