- Oh.

03:02.884 --> 03:04.617
- Uh... yeah.
- Yeah.

03:04.642 --> 03:06.184
- Okay, sure.
- Thanks.

03:06.220 --> 03:07.219
Thank you.

03:07.254 --> 03:08.553
You got her? Okay.

03:11.092 --> 03:12.859
Geez, y-you see that?

03:12.884 --> 03:14.559
I mean, she just
swooped in and took her.

03:14.595 --> 03:16.194
It was a little rude.

03:16.230 --> 03:17.629
Well, don't you go play with the twins?

03:17.664 --> 03:19.818
Well, they're sleeping,
so I guess I'm on my own.

03:19.843 --> 03:21.433
Look, you want a play date so bad,

03:21.468 --> 03:24.436
