03:28.144 --> 03:29.341
Well, it's kind of a perfect match.

03:29.376 --> 03:31.443
You want to hang out with
kids, he has no parents.

03:31.478 --> 03:33.512
Yeah, I know. I'm just...

03:34.574 --> 03:36.978
