for some stranger-baby.

05:23.158 --> 05:25.291
Don't you listen to her.

05:26.271 --> 05:28.004
Jasper?

05:30.314 --> 05:32.080
Knock-knock. (CHUCKLES)

05:32.135 --> 05:33.789
Who's there? I'm just kidding.

05:33.814 --> 05:35.233
Jasper?

05:35.269 --> 05:36.434
Hey, hey, bud.

05:37.960 --> 05:39.271
Oh, look at you.

05:39.827 --> 05:41.702
