SHOUTING, WEAPONS FIRING)

05:44.311 --> 05:46.344
Uh, killing Nazis, huh?

05:46.710 --> 05:48.784
Yeah. Don't have any
problem with that, no, sir.

05:48.809 --> 05:50.382
