important babies to tend to.

09:24.296 --> 09:25.504
It's no problem.

09:25.529 --> 09:29.132
Hey, gals. Uh, just burned
some dirty diapers on the lawn.

09:29.168 --> 09:31.518
Woman, oh,<i> woman,</i> is it hot out!

09:31.543 --> 09:32.936
