being a full-on gender-friender,

09:42.147 --> 09:45.015
then yes, I'm 100% full of crap.

09:45.050 --> 09:46.350
CAROL: You know, Tandy,

09:46.385 --> 09:49.019
there's more to being a
feminist than just talk.

09:49.054 --> 09:51.255
