10:10.670 --> 10:13.010
Nice, even strokes.

10:13.045 --> 10:15.245
Just go with the grain, bud.

10:15.281 --> 10:17.281
Again, this is not
the normal shave area,

10:17.316 --> 10:19.873
but for our purposes,
this makes the most sense.

10:19.898 --> 10:22.185
You know, because you don't have
any hair on your face, and...

10:22.221 --> 10:23.954
Melissa likes my mustache

10:23.989 --> 10:26.023
