10:26.758 --> 10:29.326
You're never gonna forget this, bud.

10:29.814 --> 10:31.614
We share a sacred bond now.

10:31.664 --> 10:32.764
Shave brothers.

10:33.852 --> 10:36.639
Or, shave father and
son, if, you know...

10:36.664 --> 10:38.035
